1. *Glave* su mi se začešlale. (My hair got tangled.)
2. On je pregledao *glave* učenika. (He checked the heads of the pupils.)
3. *Glavu* je namestio na vratima. (He placed his head on the door.)
4. Ona je podigla *glavu* i pogledala ga. (She raised her head and looked at him.)
5. *Glave* smo prekrili platnenim čarapama. (We covered our heads with cloth socks.)
6. On je pobedio sa *glavu* i rep. (He won with head and tail.)